HEADWORD: Amon-Ra
<hw>Amon-Ra</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the ancient Egyptian sun
god; supreme god of the universe in whom Amen and Ra were combined;
principal deity during Theban supremacy.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Amen-Ra</syn>⟦br⟧
